                                </p>
                            </additions>
                            <decoDesc>
                                <p>Main text in brown and black ink, rubrics in red.</p>
                                <decoNote type="initials">
                                    <p>
                                        <locus from="1r" to="1r" scheme="folios"/>: opening puzzle initial S over 7 lines in blue and red with flourishing in the same colours. The same type of initial introduces Books 4, 6, 8, and 10, while the other books are introduced by plain initials. <locus from="7r" to="187r" scheme="folios"/>: plain initials for paragraphs and chapters over 3-4 lines alternating in red and blue, occasionally with some penwork decoration.</p>
